{
  "id": "RAW_161f9c",
  "title": "【第 3586 期】从规范看 JavaScript 数组：隐藏的对象属性",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651277413&idx=1&sn=6cd7cd4a8dce0820aaca7d58b53af513",
  "date": "2025-09-12 00:02:00",
  "author": "前端早读课",
  "siteName": "前端早读课",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f2e0aa3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FmeG6Vo0Mevjf551MEoowb7wXsayQSibVPvJFFhrkep8ameDdrUucbh5w9m0hAiaiaYrv8JXr8icYsSCnzydKYN7rSg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">前言</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">探讨了 JavaScript 数组的独特性质，指出根据 ECMAScript 规范，JavaScript 数组实际上是对象。今日前端早读课文章由 @Brandon Rozek 分享，@飘飘编译。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">译文从这开始～～</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">根据 ECMAScript 规范，JavaScript 数组其实是 “特殊的对象”。所以，如果我们把它当成 C 语言里的那种数组来理解，就可能遇到一些让人摸不着头脑的行为。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277349&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f57c7d263f39196f4718219d0353faa4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3582期】Node.js Type Stripping 背后的设计取舍\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3582期】Node.js Type Stripping 背后的设计取舍</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">让我们来玩一玩。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">概念一：JavaScript 数组并非连续的</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">先看这个数组：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;let x = [0, 1, 2];</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">很自然地，</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">x.length</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;等于 3。要判断某个索引是否存在，可以用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">in</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;操作符。</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;3 in x // 结果是 false</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果访问第 3 个索引，结果是&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">undefined</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x[3] // 结果是 undefined</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在我们跳过索引 3，直接给索引 4 赋值：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x[4] = 4;</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这时再看&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">length</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;属性，会发现数组长度变成了 5。</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x.length // 结果是 5</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">但注意，第 3 个索引依然不存在：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;3 in x // 结果是 false</span></code></pre>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">概念二：显式 undefined 与 隐式 undefined</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚才我们看到&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">x[3]</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的值是&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">undefined</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。那么如果我们手动把它设成&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">undefined</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;会怎样？</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x[3] = undefined;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;3 in x // 结果是 true</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，显式赋值为&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">undefined</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和索引本身不存在是不一样的！不过，这个区别并不总是会被利用。比如在&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">for-of</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;循环中，它就不在乎。</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x = [0, 1, 2];</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x[4] = 4;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;for (a of x) {</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;console.log(a)</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">打印结果是：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;0</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;1</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;2</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;undefined</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;4</span></code></pre>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">概念三：数组索引其实是字符串</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">既然数组有&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">length</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;属性，而且我们一直在用数字来访问元素，那是不是意味着数组的索引就是数字呢？</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;\"0\" in [\"a\", \"b\"] // 结果是 true</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">看起来在幕后发生了一些类型转换的 “魔法”。根据 ECMAScript 规范，数组的索引必须严格小于&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2^32</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。那如果超过了会怎样呢？</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;let x = [0];</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x[4294967296] = true</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x // 结果是 [ 0, '4294967296': true ]</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这时它不再被当作数组元素，而是被当作一个普通的键值对。既然这样，我们当然也可以往数组里存放任意数据：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x.name = \"Brandon\"</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x // 结果是 [ 0, '4294967296': true, name: 'Brandon' ]</span></code></pre>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">把数组看作对象</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">当我们把数组当成对象来看待时，一切就更容易理解了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277268&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4d8811545f55bfdcf3a4b96e082c2b42&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3574期】可以这样写 JavaScript？！ES2025 新语法糖\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3574期】可以这样写 JavaScript？！ES2025 新语法糖</a></span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;let x = [0, 1, 2];</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;x[4] = 4;</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在内部，这对应的其实是这样一个对象：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\"0\": 0,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\"1\": 1,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\"2\": 2,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\"4\": 4</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">从这个对象可以看到，键其实都是字符串，而且第 3 个键（索引 3）根本不存在。那如果我们显式设置&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">x[5] = undefined</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;呢？</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"0\": 0,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"1\": 1,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"2\": 2,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"4\": 4,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;\"5\": undefined</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样，第 5 个键就存在了，只不过它的值是&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">undefined</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。同时，如果我们访问一个不存在的键，也会得到&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">undefined</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">数组的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">length</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是对象中最大的 “数字型” 键（前提是还没超过大小限制）。当我们用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">for-of</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;来遍历数组时，实际上就是从&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"0\"</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;一直遍历到&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">length</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;for (a of x) {</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;console.log(a);</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;}</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">等价于：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;console.log(x[0]);</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;console.log(x[1]);</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;console.log(x[2]);</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;console.log(x[3]);</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;console.log(x[4]);</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;console.log(x[5]);</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是所谓的 “特殊对象”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:0px !important;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">关于本文</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">译者：@飘飘</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者：@Brandon Rozek</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文：<a href=\"https://brandonrozek.com/blog/cursed-knowledge-javascript-arrays-are-objects/\" target=\"_blank\">https://brandonrozek.com/blog/cursed-knowledge-javascript-arrays-are-objects/</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深入探讨了 JavaScript 数组作为“特殊对象”的本质，通过分析其非连续性、索引字符串化及显式/隐式 undefined 的区别，帮助开发者从 ECMAScript 规范视角理解数组的底层工作原理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深入探讨了 JavaScript 数组作为“特殊对象”的本质，通过分析其非连续性、索引字符串化及显式/隐式 undefined 的区别，帮助开发者从 ECMAScript 规范视角理解数组的底层工作原理。",
  "summary": "本文从 ECMAScript 规范出发，揭示了 JavaScript 数组并非传统意义上的连续内存结构，而是具有独特行为的“特殊对象”。文章通过三个核心概念进行了详细阐述：首先，它指出 JavaScript 数组并非连续，通过跳过索引赋值，数组长度会增加，但中间索引并不实际存在，这与 C 语言等传统数组的概念形成鲜明对比。其次，文章区分了显式将元素赋值为`undefined`和索引本身不存在的差异，前者会使该索引实际存在，而后者则不会，尽管在某些遍历场景下两者表现一致。最后，文章强调 JavaScript 数组的索引本质上是字符串，当数字索引超出 ECMAScript 规范定义的数组索引最大值（2^32-1）时，它们会被视为普通的对象属性。通过将数组视为带有`length`属性和数字键的对象，文章成功解释了这些看似反直觉的行为，极大地提升了读者对 JavaScript 数组底层机制的理解，对于编写更健壮、更符合预期的 JavaScript 代码具有重要的指导意义。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "JavaScript 数组并非连续存储结构，其长度由最大数字型键决定，中间可能存在空洞。",
      "explanation": "这与传统编程语言的数组概念不同，理解其内部实现有助于解释跳跃赋值后数组长度变化但中间索引不存在的现象，避免开发者产生误解。"
    },
    {
      "point": "显式赋值`undefined`与索引不存在有本质区别，前者使得索引实际存在于数组中。",
      "explanation": "尽管两者在访问时都返回`undefined`，但通过`in`操作符可揭示其内部差异，这对于精确控制数组状态和理解遍历行为至关重要。"
    },
    {
      "point": "数组索引在底层被视为字符串，超出特定范围的数字键会退化为普通对象属性。",
      "explanation": "这一机制揭示了 JavaScript 数组作为“特殊对象”的本质，帮助开发者理解为何数组可以拥有非数字属性，并更好地利用其灵活性进行编程。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "根据 ECMAScript 规范，JavaScript 数组其实是 \"特殊的对象\"。",
    "所以，显式赋值为 undefined 和索引本身不存在是不一样的！",
    "这时它不再被当作数组元素，而是被当作一个普通的键值对。",
    "当我们把数组当成对象来看待时，一切就更容易理解了。",
    "数组的 length 是对象中最大的 \"数字型\" 键（前提是还没超过大小限制）。"
